    @Deprecated
 @FunctionalInterface
public interface BuiltinCapacitiesProvider
    This interface represents a provider of built-in capacities. The built-in capacities are assumed to be provided by the runtime platform.

        Applies the given callback on the built-in capacities for the given agent.
        Parameters:
        agent - the agent for which the built-in capacities must be retreived.
        skillMappingCallback - the callback function for mapping a capacity and a skill. The first argument is the agent. The second argument is the builtin capacity. The third argument is the skill instance.
